<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Featured Article of the Month</span></strong><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: small;"><br /></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/user/pontia1121?feature=mhee#p/a/u/2/WkqJxXUVAUc"><img height="176" width="284" src="/images/stories/DSC_0469.jpg" alt="DSC_0469" style="float: left; border: #898276 solid;" /></a><br /><span style="color: #000000;">On Saturday, May 21, the Pontian Greek Society of Chicago hosted a lecture by Professor Dan Georgakas</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="color: #000000;"> entitled <em>The Smyrna Death March of 1922 </em>at Duke Realty Corp. Auditorium in Rosemont, Illinois.</span>  <br /><br /><a href="/images/stories/Smyrna_Speech_gr11.pdf">Click here</a> <span style="color: #000000;">for lecture in Greek<br />Μετάφραση Γιάννη Κωσταντινίδη -γραμματέα Συλλόγου<br /><br /><br />Click on the picture to watch <strong>Part I</strong> of the lecture</span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">Click <a target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/user/pontia1121?feature=mhee#p/a/u/1/4wZGS2lNqNY">here</a> for<strong> Part II</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="color: #000000;">Click <a target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/user/pontia1121?feature=mhee#p/a/u/0/FcwUh1uP_f8">here</a> for<strong> Part III<br /><em><a target="_blank" href="/images/stories/Greek_Star_June_2_2011_pg_81.pdf">The Greek Star</a></em> Article*<br /><a target="_blank" href="http://www.armenianweekly.com/2011/06/15/the-smyrna-death-march-of-1922/"><em>Armenian Weekly</em> </a>Article**</strong></span></span></span></span></p>
